node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Míriam Bonastre Tur on July 27, 2021. May be an illustration of 1 person.

node.text:
Hello! 💚

Don't worry! The book version of HOOKY will be the same as the webtoon! But I had to redraw the first 10 episodes (60 pages) because I lost the original files when my old computer broke 😭
It was a lot of work redrawing all these pages, but also an interesting and fun exercise, and I wanted to share a little sneak peek with you. I can't deny that I kinda miss the old art of the first episodes, and I'm sure that some of you miss it too. It looked fresh and dynamic. But my current art style is more aligned with who I am today. And I think it looks more adorable too. 
I hope you like it!

Also, I wanted to remind you that HOOKY will be out soon and that you can preorder a LIMITED signed edition on @barnesandnoble @booksamillion or through your local indie bookstore on indiebound.org
Enter for your prize pack here hmhbooks.com/hookypreorder

#hooky #hookywebtoon #WEBTOON #miriambonastre @clarionbooks @webtoonofficial

node.text:
Hey! ✨🎪

I had a ton of work today! But I was feeling really bad and I was unable to concentrate, so I drew this as a warm-up. It kinda worked and I got more inspired! I managed to finish a few things so I decided to color this before going to bed. I hope you like it 🥰

The little dog is based on my own dog, Titu, who passed away last year 💔  My mum always insists that I should use Titu as a character in my comics, so maybe I will do it in the future 🐶

#miriambonastre

node.text:
Only two months until HOOKY is here! I can't believe it! 😳💖

Hello again, more summer vibes for you all! 
I thought it would be cool to draw Dani and Dorian with their swimsuits from the beach episode! It's been a long time so drawing them like this again was super fun! ☀️ 

The book is out on 9/7 and you can preorder it now! Everyone who preorders gets a prize-pack that includes an enamel pin of Carlo, a signed book plate and 'Nico's Love Letter', an extra story in digital format. Find more details and enter with your proof of purchase at hmhbooks.com/hookypreorder

You can also find the link on my stories highlights.

💖💖💖
#hooky #hookywebtoon #WEBTOON #miriambonastre @clarionbooks @webtoonofficial

node.text:
Just wanted to post something cute with summer vibes! ☀️🍦

And I also brought the dress on the left but I was too lazy to take pictures of myself to draw an outfit of the day, so here it is a random girl wearing it 😌 I hope you like it.

I've been working a lot lately. I'm trying to get tan but I only go to the beach on weekends even if I actually life in a beach town. I'm just too busy 😭 But I've been eating a lot of ice cream. What is your favorite ice cream flavor? My favorite one is dark chocolate, but I also like blueberries and cheesecake 😳

Well see ya! 💖

#miriambonastre

node.text:
Spring witches! 🌼🥰

This was so fun to draw! I wanted to draw something seasonal before spring ends 😳 I hope you like it!

Lately I've been working a lot on the printed version of Hooky. I had to redraw some chapters and I did some extra content exclusively for the book, so now I'm used again to draw Dani and Dorian as little kids! 🥺 I love their older versions too, but they were just so cute at the beginning!

The book is out on 9/7 and you can preorder it now! Everyone who preorders gets a prize pack that includes Nico's Love Letter, an extra story in digital format. Find more details and enter with your proof of purchase at hmhbooks.com/hookypreorder

You can also find the link on my stories highlights.

💖💖💖
#hooky #hookywebtoon #WEBTOON #miriambonastre @clarionbooks @webtoonofficial

node.text:
Hello! Long time no see! 😳✨

I''ve been working a lot lately, and it seems that I will keep working a lot during summer. But I'm actually super motivated! 🍤 I also have some news that I'm gonna share very soon 😌

I'll try to keep this alive tho! I want to be able to draw things outside work and to show you. And this is the only way I can communicate with you all, since I'm not very social on my social media, and I miss you! 😭

So yes... It's Tecna's time! The last character from Winx Club 🧚‍♀️

I have to admit that I wasn't very excited to draw her since the futuristic style is not my cup of tea, BUT I actually enjoyed this A LOT. This is one of my favorites 😳 Which one do you like the most in my style?

#winx #winxclub #winxtecna #miriambonastre

I'm excited to announce our HOOKY U.S. preorder campaign! Order now (or by 9/6) and you can get a limited edition prize-pack.

✨To enter fill out the entry form and find more details here: hmhbooks.com/hookypreorder

I designed a super cute enamel pin of Carlo 🐸 and you'll also get a signed plate from me. Oh, and everyone, INCLUDING INTERNATIONAL ORDERS, can get access to this exclusive digital content I created for you, the little story "Nico's Love Letter" 😳💖

I'm super excited about this (not canon) new story about the high school life of the kids! I drew a few panels a while ago (you can find it here on Instagram), and I always wanted to continue it, so this was the perfect opportunity! I hope you like it!

⚠️ If you already preordered a copy of HOOKY you can still enter your proof of purchase to get the swag. 

@clarionbooks @webtoonofficial

#hooky #hookywebtoon #WEBTOON #miriambonastre

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Míriam Bonastre Tur on April 05, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text:
Another outfit of the day! 😳 As you know, I love drawing these from time to time and I hope you like it too. It's so relaxing for me. You can also see my new bedroom in the background ✨

I used this to make my first tiktok. I posted it on my tiktok account (@miriambonastre) and also on reels. I'm pretty shy and nervous about this!! It was kinda difficult 😢 But it was very fun to do, so I will make more for sure.
Tell me what you think! 💖

#ootd #miriambootd #miriambonastre

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Míriam Bonastre Tur on March 30, 2021. May be an anime-style image of one or more people.

node.text:
Stella! ✨🌞✨
I hope you like it! 
Who should I draw next?

I'm happy because I've been very productive these days, and that's despite the fact that I recently downloaded TikTok. I never thought that app was for me, but the truth is that I am quite hooked. I haven't posted anything yet but I'm seriously considering it. I think that format allows you to do very creative and fun things. Although maybe at first it will be difficult for me to get the hang of it. If I post something there I will let you know! Meanwhile you can still follow me on TikTok if you want. I'm also @miriambonastre there 😳

#winx #winxclub #winxstella #miriambonastre
